cdata.name: Gron Digital
cdata.desc:
Gron Digital is a Gambling and Betting Platform. It allows participants to access the platform supported games using cryptocurrencies as payment. The transactions performed on Gron Digital are processed through smart contracts in order to exclude 3rd parties.

The Platform is operated by a utility token – called GRO. The GRO is used by participants in exchange for value and services they provide. Service providers, bookmakers, casino operators, affiliates, regulators and players are a few examples of the participants within the Gron Digital eco-system.
